11import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Rop.Cox.Calc        as Rop
12import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Rop.Cox.Empty       as Rop

21-- | Relational operators with content calculation.
22ropsCox :: (K.CContent c) => [C.Rop c]
23ropsCox    = Rop.ropsCoxCalc
24          ++ Rop.ropsCoxEmpty
25          ++ Rop.ropsCoxFilter
26          ++ Rop.ropsCoxGadget
27          ++ Rop.ropsCoxRange
28          ++ Rop.ropsTypeClock
